snippet.title: Best VGM 685 - Heimdall 2 - Reflections
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 567 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PAU7aZ_Pz4c

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Amiga CD32 / DOS
Heimdall 2 (1994)
Reflections
Martin Iveson
